au.edu.rmit.tzar.api

Interface ProjectSpec

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ProjectSpecImpl

    public interface ProjectSpec
    Specification for a single Tzar project. Along with the model code, and the libraries pointed to by the libraries map, this contains enough information to create a set of Tzar runs for this project.
